checklist.Text: Remove Picogreen Kit from fridge, loosen cover.
Let kit contents equilibriate at room temperature for 20 minutes.
Only open lid a crack to protect Picogreen reagent from light.
Don gloves and swab work area with nucleic acid decontaminant.
Wrap 50mL tube with aluminum foil.
Pipette 19.9mL of Picogreen Buffer into foil wrapped tube.
Pipette 100ÂµL of concentrated Picogreen reagent into the foil wrapped tube.
Vortex tube, let bubbles settle.
Pour contents into reservoir.
Cover reservoir with foil.
Tear off a piece of foil sufficient to cover 96-well plate.
Turn plate.
Use 8-channel pipettor to load 185 ÂµL of Picogreen mix into wells in column 1.
Use 8-channel pipettor to load 185 ÂµL of Picogreen mix into wells in column 2.
Load 195 ÂµL of Picrogreen mix into column 3.
Load 195 ÂµL of Picrogreen mix into column 4.
Load 195 ÂµL of Picrogreen mix into column 5.
Load 195 ÂµL of Picrogreen mix into column 6.
Load 195 ÂµL of Picrogreen mix into column 7.
Load 195 ÂµL of Picrogreen mix into column 8.
Load 195 ÂµL of Picrogreen mix into column 9.
Load 195 ÂµL of Picrogreen mix into column 10.
Load 195 ÂµL of Picrogreen mix into column 11.
Load 195 ÂµL of Picrogreen mix into column 12.
Turn plate.
Load 15 ÂµL of Picogreen mix into well A1.
Vortex clear 0 ng/mL tube.
Load 15 ÂµL clear 0 ng/mL standard into well A2.
Vortex green 5 ng/mL tube.
Load 15 ÂµL green 5 ng/mL standard into well B1.
Load 15 ÂµL green 5 ng/mL standard into well B2.
Vortex blue 10 ng/mL tube.
Load 15 ÂµL blue 10 ng/mL standard into well C1.
Load 15 ÂµL blue 10 ng/mL standard into well C2.
Vortex lilac 20 ng/mL tube.
Load 15 ÂµL lilac 20 ng/mL standard into well D1.
Load 15 ÂµL lilac 20 ng/mL standard into well D2.
Vortex red 40 ng/mL tube.
Load 15 ÂµL red 40 ng/mL standard into well E1.
Load 15 ÂµL red 40 ng/mL standard into well E2.
Vortex orange 60 ng/mL tube.
Load 15 ÂµL orange 60 ng/mL standard into well F1.
Load 15 ÂµL orange 60 ng/mL standard into well F2.
Vortex brown 80 ng/mL tube.
Load 15 ÂµL brown 80 ng/mL standard into well G1.
Load 15 ÂµL brown 80 ng/mL standard into well G2.
Vortex yellow 100 ng/mL tube.
Load 15 ÂµL yellow 100 ng/mL standard into well H1.
Load 15 ÂµL yellow 100 ng/mL standard into well H2.
Remove samples from incubator.
Place tubes in 5 X 10 tube rack on benchtop.
Add 5 ÂµL of sample 1 to well A3.
Add 5 ÂµL of sample 2 to well B3.
Add 5 ÂµL of sample 3 to well C3.
Add 5 ÂµL of sample 4 to well D3.
Add 5 ÂµL of sample 5 to well E3.
Add 5 ÂµL of sample 6 to well F3.
Add 5 ÂµL of sample 7 to well G3.
Add 5 ÂµL of sample 8 to well H3.
Add 5 ÂµL of sample 9 to well A4.
Add 5 ÂµL of sample 10 to well B4.
Add 5 ÂµL of sample 11 to well C4.
Add 5 ÂµL of sample 12 to well D4.
Add 5 ÂµL of sample 13 to well E4.
Add 5 ÂµL of sample 14 to well F4.
Add 5 ÂµL of sample 15 to well G4.
Add 5 ÂµL of sample 16 to well H4.
Cover plate with foil.
